Interface SolverDataSource

public interface SolverDataSource

An interface to be implemented by the classes that manage the user interaction. An object of type solver should be created and then the methods in this interface will be called on the UI class object to get the Constructions and Tiles. This methods will be called after a call to initialize is made on the
